  },
]

---

<LayoutPaginas title="Patagonia Courses | Rock Climbing Course" description="">
  <div class="container text-start px-3 px-lg-5">

    <Titulo title=' Patagonia Courses' />

    <div class="container text-center px-lg-5">
      <div class="row">
        <div class="col-auto col-lg-6 py-2 px-0">
          <nav aria-label="breadcrumb">
            <ol class="breadcrumb my-2">
              <li class="breadcrumb-item"><a class="text-decoration-none text-body-secondary" href="/">Home</a></li>
              <li class="breadcrumb-item active"><a class="text-decoration-none text-body-secondary" href=/#courses>Courses</a></li>
              <li class="breadcrumb-item active"><a class="text-decoration-none text-body-secondary" href=/courses/rock-climbing-course>Rock Climbing</a></li>
            </ol>
          </nav>
          <h3 class="fs-3 fw-normal text-start text-body-secondary border-top pt-3">Rock Climbing Course Level I and II</h3>
          <div class="texto fw-light ls-1 fs-5 text-start fst-italic text-body-secondary pe-0 pe-lg-4">
            <p>
              The objective of the courses are to immerse the student in the world of rock climbing.  They are designed for those people who are beginning and also for those who have previous knowledge in this discipline. We will form and build a solid foundation with regard to safety knowledge in rock climbing and develop climbers that can continue on with the desired skills, fluency and autonomy in many different aspects of sport climbing. We will also help achieve the technical objectives of the people who practice this sport.</br>
              <b>Course duration:</b></br>
              - 4 theoretical classes</br>
              - 5 full-day outdoor classes on rock</br>
              - 1 day of theoretical and practical exam
              </p>
              <a href="/itineraries/courses/RockClimbingCourse.pdf" target="_blank" class="fs-5 fw-normal link-secondary fst-normal text-body-secondary icon-link icon-link-hover link-offset-2-hover link-underline link-underline-opacity-0 link-underline-opacity-100-hover" role="button" aria-label="Download Itinerary">DOWNLOAD ITINERARY</a>
              <i class="fa-solid fa-file-arrow-down bi text-decoration-none ms-2"></i>
          </div>    
        </div>
        
        <Slider miArray={fotos} />

      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</LayoutPaginas>

<style>
  .texto {
    font-family: "Helvetica Neue",Helvetica,Arial,sans-serif;
    letter-spacing: 1px; 
  }
</style>
